This is a Council proposal to re-elect the following individuals to the Orca Governance Council for the 2024 term:
(i) Cortina;
(ii) Hart Lambur;
(iii) Chris Montagano;
(iv) Larry Sukernik;
(v) Wes Tang-Wymer; and
(vi) Lakshman Sankar.

Further information regarding this proposal can be found here:  https://forums.orca.so/t/orca-governance-council-2024-re-elections/288
